        "subject": "LU-2182 llapi: Expand layout api to verify against a target file system",
        "message": "LU-2182 llapi: Expand layout api to verify against a target file system\n\nBesides validating the layout users create against the limits of\nLustre add additional functions that can validate the layout\nagainst the target file system. To do this two function are added.\nThe function llapi_layout_pool_absent can be used to ensure the\nlayout's pool is actually present on the file system. The second\nfunction llapi_layout_ost_index_valid ensures that the user\nspecified OST index supplied matches to a real OST on the file\nsystem. This method also test if the OST index belongs to the\nlayout's pool if one is present.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: Ie2eb1538881d3e6b070c45d50a4a8c3dd87052c7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
